*** Context ***
+ Clear Workspace
+ A project is created in the workspace without Execution Environment

*** Actions ***
- Open the main.lua file
- Declare a local function with a parameter
- Re-use the parameter in the function
- Re-use it out of the function
- Click once on the parameter in the function declaration

*** Assertions ***
# All occurences of the parameter in the function and its declaration are highlighted
# The parameter out of the function is not highlighted
